1 packet shredded coconut
1 tin Tinned Mango
1 packet Toasted Vanilla Almond Muesli
1 packet Original Thick & Creamy Yoghurt

Heat a large frying pan over medium-high heat. Toast shredded coconut until golden, 2-3 minutes.

Drain tinned mango and
thinly slice.

In a serving bowl, add a layer of toasted vanilla almond muesli (store leftover muesli in an airtight container). Top with a dollop of original thick & creamy yoghurt, some mango and toasted coconut.

FRESH TIP: Heat a large frying pan over medium-high heat. Toast your favourite nut or seed tossing, until golden, 2-3 minutes. Once cooled slightly, sprinkle over!